        "end": 44.403
      },
      {
        "segment": "We perceive the query now.",
        "start_offset": 397,
        "end_offset": 423,
        "start": 44.703,
        "end": 50.463
      },
      {
        "segment": "To give this in your terms is misleading for there are, shall we say, visual aids or training aids available in fourth density which automatically aid the entity in polarization while cutting down extremely upon the quick effect of catalyst.",
        "start_offset": 424,
        "end_offset": 665,
        "start": 53.043,
        "end": 111.627
      },
      {
        "segment": "Thus the density above yours must take up more space/time.",
        "start_offset": 666,
        "end_offset": 724,
        "start": 114.728,
        "end": 128.368
      },
      {
        "segment": "The percentage of service to others of positively oriented entities will harmoniously approach in intention.",
        "start_offset": 725,
        "end_offset": 837,
        "start": 130.689,
        "end": 161.491
      },
      {
        "segment": "The qualifications for fifth density, however, involve understanding.",
        "start_offset": 838,
        "end_offset": 907,
        "start": 164.431,
        "end": 183.432
      },
      {
        "segment": "This then, becomes the primary qualification for graduation from fourth to fifth density.",
        "start_offset": 908,
        "end_offset": 997,
        "start": 183.452,
        "end": 204.973
      },
      {
        "segment": "To achieve this graduation the entity must be able to understand the actions, the movements, and the dance.",
        "start_offset": 998,
        "end_offset": 1105,
        "start": 207.474,
        "end": 236.855
      },
      {
        "segment": "There is no percentage describable which measures this understanding.",
        "start_offset": 1106,
        "end_offset": 1175,
        "start": 239.676,
        "end": 253.177
      },
      {
        "segment": "It is a measure of efficiency of perception.",
        "start_offset": 1176,
        "end_offset": 1220,
        "start": 254.657,
        "end": 264.737
      },
      {
        "segment": "It may be measured by light.",
        "start_offset": 1221,
        "end_offset": 1249,
        "start": 266.577,
        "end": 272.118
      },
      {
        "segment": "The ability to love, accept, and use a certain intensity of light thus creates the requirement for both positive and negative fourth to fifth harvesting.",
